# TLIS
## TikTok Luxury Intelligence System

TLIS (TikTok Luxury Intelligence System) is an AI-powered platform designed to help creators, agencies, brands and businesses research, organize, create, schedule and manage premium TikTok content workflows from one secure dashboard.

---

# Vision

To become the leading AI-powered workflow platform for luxury digital marketing, premium audience intelligence, content automation and lawful online research.

